---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "About Us (Profile & Business Overview) | Wa-Node";
const description = "Hirozumi Takano's professional profile at Wa-Node. We combine 20+ years of IT engineering expertise with behavioral psychology insights as an Industrial Counselor and universal accessibility perspectives. Delivering conversion funnel design and strategic co-piloting.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} lang="en">
  <main>
    <section class="section about-hero">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <span class="eyebrow">Professional Background</span>
        <h1>About Wa-Node</h1>
        <p class="lead">Providing conversion-optimized web production and strategic business co-piloting,<br class="pc-only" />seamlessly blending 20+ years of solid IT engineering with behavioral psychology and accessibility.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section message">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="message-content reveal">
          <div class="content-left">
            <h2>Founder's Message</h2>
            <h3 class="catch-copy">"Because psychological friction<br class="sp-only"/>turns away the user's heart."</h3>
            <p>With over 20 years in the IT industry, I have navigated numerous projects ranging from large-scale system architecture to bespoke web design. Through this journey, I reached a definitive conviction: <strong>"No technology, regardless of its brilliance, delivers true value unless it is deeply empathetic to human psychology."</strong></p>
            <p>Having integrated a personal perspective through my life in a wheelchair, this belief has grown even more resolute. Designing navigation paths that anyone can operate intuitively and without hesitation is not simply an act of "kindness"; it is a "technical responsibility" to maximize business results.</p>
            <p>Wa-Node offers comprehensive support, spanning from psychology-driven web design to operational streamlining through AI and ICT. Bringing "Nagi" (tranquility) to your business and securing your next step with certainty is my ultimate mission.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="content-right">
            <div class="profile-image-wrap">
              <img src="/images/avatar.webp" alt="Wa-Node Representative Hirozumi Takano" />
              <p class="name-jp">高野 紘純</p>
              <p class="name-en">Hirozumi Takano</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section profile-details">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-title">
          <span class="eyebrow">Profile & Skills</span>
          <h2>Bespoke Web Design & Strategic Partnership</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="story-box reveal">
          <h3>The Fusion of Tech and Psychology</h3>
          <p>Since qualifying as an Industrial Counselor in 2002, I have spent decades studying the psychology of individuals and organizations alongside my career as an IT engineer. Approaching projects from both the technological and psychological fronts is Wa-Node's greatest strength.</p>
          <p>My personal path in overcoming physical challenges has given me a unique perspective: how to harness cutting-edge generative AI and automation technologies with maximum efficiency, while never losing the human touch.</p>
          <p>From legacy system integration to modern Astro, React, and generative AI systems, I design and build solutions that truly work in the real world.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="qual-grid reveal">
          <div class="qual-item highlight-border">
            <h4>Web Production & ICT Technology</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>20+ years of system engineering & web development</li>
              <li>HTML5 / CSS3 / JavaScript (React, Astro)</li>
              <li>Generative AI (ChatGPT, Claude) system design & prompt engineering</li>
              <li>Workflow automation (LINE APIs, Google Apps Script, etc.)</li>
              <li>Information Security Management / Applied Information Technology Engineer</li>
              <li>Cisco Certifications (CCNA, etc.) / Network Design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="qual-item">
            <h4>Psychology & Accessibility (Core Foundations)</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Industrial Counselor (Certified in 2002)</li>
              <li>JADP Certified Mental Health Counselor / Senior Psychological Counselor</li>
              <li>Barrier-Free Residential Environment Advisor</li>
              <li>Universal Design & Web Accessibility Architecture</li>
              <li>Bookkeeping Grade 2 / Corporate Financial Management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section business-overview">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-title">
          <span class="eyebrow">Overview</span>
          <h2>Business Overview</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="overview-table-wrap reveal">
          <table class="overview-table">
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <th>Business Name</th>
                <td>和-Node (Wa-Node)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>Representative</th>
                <td>Hirozumi Takano</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>Location</th>
                <td>2347-1 Imawatari, Kani City, Gifu, 509-0207, Japan</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>Services</th>
                <td>
                  <ul>
                    <li><strong>Psychology-driven Web Design</strong>: Strategic funnel architecture & development (LPs & Websites)</li>
                    <li><strong>Business Co-pilot (Monthly)</strong>: Strategic partnership, ongoing optimization & maintenance</li>
                    <li><strong>ICT & App Integration</strong>: LINE Mini App integration, automation tooling</li>
                    <li><strong>Corporate Support & Psychology</strong>: Corporate communication & specialized inquiry channels</li>
                    <li><strong>KDP Publishing Support</strong>: Global brand building via Amazon Kindle Self-Publishing</li>
                  </ul>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>Service Areas</th>
                <td>Global/Nationwide (Fully remote support), Tokai Region (Gifu/Aichi) for in-person consultations</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section reliability">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="reliability-box reveal">
          <h2>Foundation of Trust & Security</h2>
          <div class="trust-grid">
            <div class="trust-item">
              <img src="/images/security-action-one-star.webp" alt="SECURITY ACTION Badge" class="trust-badge" />
              <p>We are officially committed to carrying out strict information security measures.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-content">
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Pursuit of Production Quality</strong>: We promise high-precision navigation design grounded in behavioral psychology.</li>
                <li><strong>Professional Ethics</strong>: We strictly adhere to confidentiality as an Industrial Counselor and enforce rigorous data management.</li>
                <li><strong>Transparent Pricing</strong>: No unexpected charges or opaque billing without prior agreement.</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="policy-links">
                <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="/security-policy/">Information Security Policy</a>
                <a href="/terms/">Terms of Service</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section contact-teaser">
      <div class="section-inner text-center">
        <h2 class="reveal">Unifying Tech and Psychology into a Seamless Conversion Funnel.</h2>
        <p class="reveal">During the first free consultation (30-60 min), we will map out your current challenges and vision.<br />Please feel free to share your story.</p>
        <div class="btns reveal" style="justify-content: center;">
          <a href="/en/contact/" class="btn primary">Start Free Consultation & Request a Draft Mock-up</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdfcf9 0%, #f7f1e6 100%);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .about-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-deep); }
  
  .message-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .catch-copy {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .message-content p { margin-bottom: 20px; color: #444; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  
  .profile-image-wrap {
    text-align: center;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .profile-image-wrap img {
    width: 220px;
    height: 220px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: var(--soft);
  }
  .name-jp { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .name-en { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

  .story-box {
    background: var(--soft);
    padding: 48px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .story-box h3 { margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 800; }
  .story-box p { margin-bottom: 16px; color: #444; line-height: 1.8; }

  .qual-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .qual-item {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .qual-item.highlight-border { border: 2px solid var(--accent); }
  .qual-item h4 { margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--accent); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 800; }
  .qual-item ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .qual-item li { position: relative; padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; }
  .qual-item li::before { content: "•"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 800; }

  .overview-table-wrap {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .overview-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .overview-table th, .overview-table td {
    padding: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .overview-table th {
    background: var(--soft);
    width: 250px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  .overview-table td ul { padding-left: 20px; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .overview-table td li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .overview-table td li strong { color: var(--accent-dark); }
  .overview-table tr:last-child th, .overview-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

  .reliability-box {
    background: var(--text-deep);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 80px 60px;
    border-radius: 40px;
  }
  .reliability-box h2 { color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 40px; font-weight: 800; }
  .trust-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center; }
  .trust-badge { width: 150px; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 10px; }
  .trust-content ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .trust-content li { margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 0.95rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
  .trust-content strong { color: var(--accent); }
  
  .policy-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .policy-links a { color: #fff; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.7; transition: 0.3s; }
  .policy-links a:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--accent); }

  .text-center { text-align: center; }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .message-content, .trust-grid, .qual-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .content-right { order: -1; }
    .profile-image-wrap img { width: 160px; height: 160px; }
    .overview-table th { width: 120px; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 15px; }
    .overview-table td { padding: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .reliability-box { padding: 40px 20px; }
  }
</style>
